data.description: Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home sprawled across 2,316 square feet, complete with a yard offering privacy of no rear neighbors. The kitchen boasts granite counters, black appliances and rich dark cabinets. An expansive upstairs loft provides ample space for various activities. Notably, this property comes equipped with solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. Conveniently located to nearby shopping centers, schools, the VA hospital, Nellis AFB, and offers easy access to freeways. Experience comfort and convenience in one package!
